        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-04-09 13:46:25.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-2\n\nThis is not the right way to release.  The version we store in gerrit has to always be a snapshot version, otherwise merge builds will fail (first one will succeed, but subsequent ones will fail on the deploy step because release version will already exist in nexus).\n\nTo release sdnc/apps, just add comment \"please release\" to the most recent change on the sdnc/apps repo - that will trigger the Jenkins release build jobs.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
